SocialIcons
===========

This is a simple plugin to help you display some social icons in your site.

Icons supported so far:

- Facebook like button
- Facebook
- Twitter
- Delicious
- Reddit
- Digg


Installation
============

Install plugin from github:
$ script/plugin install git://github.com/itkin/social_icons.git -r rails3

Install social icons images and stylesheet in their respective directories
$ rails g social_icons

  images/social_icons/*
  stylesheets/social_icons.css

Load social_icons.css file in your layout(i.e. application.html.erb)
<%= stylesheet_link_tag 'social_icons' %>


Usage
============

<%= social_icons do |icon| %>
  <%= icon.facebook_like %>
  <%= icon.facebook %>
  <%= icon.twitter %>
<% end %>


